Antigonish Arena is a 2,290-seat multi-purpose arena in Antigonish, Nova Scotia, Canada. It is home to both the Junior A and Junior B Antigonish Bulldogs hockey teams. The arena was home to the St. Francis Xavier X-Men and St. Francis Xavier X-Women|X-Women hockey teams before they moved into a new on-campus Charles V. Keating Millennium Centre|arena. 
